    {
      "instruction": "<p>Add the <strong>meat-free meatballs</strong> to one side of your reserved baking tray (use <strong>tin foil</strong> to avoid mess!)</p><p>Add the <strong>chopped pepper</strong> to the other side, then put the tray in the oven for 12-15 min or until the meatballs are cooked through and the pepper has softened – these are your <strong>harissa meat-free meatballs</strong> and <strong>roasted pepper</strong></p>",
      "order": 4,
      "media": {
        "images": [
          {
