      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Meanwhile, dissolve your <strong>vegetable stock mix </strong>and the <strong>remaining</strong> <strong>harissa paste</strong> (not a fan of spice? Just add a little!) in 200ml <span class=\"text-purple\">[300ml]</span> <span class=\"text-danger\">[400ml]</span> <strong>boiled water</strong> in a large heatproof bowl</p><p>Add your <strong>couscous</strong>, cover and set aside until all the liquid has been absorbed</p>",
      "order": 5,
      "media": {
