        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Add your <strong>natural yoghurt</strong> to a separate bowl with a drizzle of <strong>olive oil</strong> and a pinch of <strong>salt</strong> and <strong>pepper</strong> – this is your <strong>seasoned yoghurt</strong></p><p>Chop the <strong>toasted</strong> <strong>cashews</strong> coarsely (only once they are cool enough to handle!)</p>",
      "order": 6,
