      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Fluff the <strong>cooked</strong> <strong>couscous</strong> with a fork, season with a grind of <strong>black</strong> <strong>pepper</strong> and mix most of the <strong>chopped parsley</strong> <strong>leaves</strong> through (save a few leaves for garnish!)</p><p>Once done, add the <strong>roasted pepper </strong>to the couscous and give it a good mix up</p>",
