    {
      "instruction": "<p>Serve the <strong>harissa meat-free meatballs</strong> over the <strong>roasted pepper couscous</strong> with the <strong>seasoned yoghurt</strong> dotted over</p><p>Garnish with the <strong>toasted chopped cashews </strong>and<strong> reserved parsley leaves</strong></p><p>Enjoy!</p>",
